snippet.title: MetaDOS: In-development Gameplay
snippet.description:
🎮MetaDOS In-development Gameplay

🔥 Battle Royale Mode: multiplayer mode with last-man-standing gameplay in a massive survival game.

⏱ Time Feature: gives players a countdown from the battle beginning till the end. Players can also collect it when participating in a battle.

💪 Squad Mode: players will unite with one another in a team of four to better their chances of avoiding eliminations.

🌐Official Channels
https://ds.gl/go
